divs: Sighting Detailsin my backyard I was watching some weird clouds with my wife.I thought it was a plane but noticed it wasnt moving. my wife walked into the house I was still ouside and decided to get the video camera. I told her to come back outside with me and watch it.it stayed in the same spot blinking for at least 5 or 6 minutes. I was really surprised because I AM A SKEPTIC AND DONT BELIEVE IN EXTRATERRESTRIALS.the object just stopped blinking and I got it on tape. I don't have the ability to transfer the tape to my computer so I cannot attatch it.sorry.
Summary: blinking light in eastern sky that did not move
